OL,5,G1600 Tipping Point
OL,6,     FBen Shephard hosts the quiz in
OL,7,     Fwhich contestants answer questions
OL,8,     Fto win turns on an arcade-style
OL,9,     Fmachine. Dropping tokens down a
OL,10,     Fchoice of four chutes, they hope
OL,11,     Fto knock piles of them off a
OL,12,     Fmoving shelf - and the more they
OL,13,     Fcollect, the greater the prize
OL,14,     Ffund. The player who has won the
OL,15,     Fleast amount is then eliminated,
OL,16,     Fand the last one standing competes
OL,17,     Ffor a #10,000 jackpot
