OL,5,G0230 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FTurkiye v USA (Kick-off 3.00am).
OL,7,     FLaura Woods presents coverage of
OL,8,     Fthe Group D match at Los Angeles
OL,9,     FStadium in Inglewood, USA. The USA
OL,10,     Fhave already won the group and
OL,11,     Fwill play in the last 32 on
OL,12,     FWednesday in Santa Clara, while
OL,13,     FTurkiye have already been
OL,14,     Feliminated following defeats to
OL,15,     FAustralia and Paraguay. Four of
OL,16,     Fthe five previous meetings between
OL,17,     Fthese nations have taken place
OL,18,     Fsince the turn of the century, and
OL,19,     Fall of them have ended in a 2-1
OL,20,     Fscoreline. Two were in favour of
OL,21,     Fthe Americans, and the other two
OL,22,     Fwent the way of the Turkish,
